# GSE 301 – Python Data Science Project

## Project Title
Student Academic Performance System

## Course
GSE 301 – Data Science and Machine Learning with Python

## Description
This project is a menu-driven Python program that manages student academic records.
It allows users to:
- View all students
- Add a new student
- Check graduation eligibility
- Identify the top-performing student
- Exit the system

The project demonstrates the use of Python data structures such as dictionaries, lists, tuples, and sets, as well as functions, conditionals, loops, and user input.

## Features
- Student data storage
- CGPA-based graduation eligibility check
- Automatic top performer detection
- Interactive menu system

